	 <title>System.BeginApplicationTransaction</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This begins an application transaction. An application transaction is
		  an optimistic transaction. It does not open locks on the requested data, but
		  performs an optimistic concurrency check prior to updating the changed data
		  from the created cache. For More information see the DAE developers guide. For
		  more information about application transactions, see the corresponding entry in
		  the Dataphor Developers guide.</para> 
